---
const features = [
  'We work inside your CRM (JobNimbus, AccuLynx, CompanyCam, or whatever you use)',
  'Carrier communication comes from your company email',
  'Your branding on every document',
  'Your clients never know we exist',
];
---

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css" />

<section id="whitelabel" class="px-5 md:px-8 py-24 max-w-page mx-auto">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-16 items-center">

    <!-- Content -->
    <div>
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-accent-teal mb-4">The Difference</div>
      <h2 class="font-heading text-[2rem] md:text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-white tracking-[-0.02em] mb-6 leading-[1.15]">
        We don't just work for you. We work as you.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-[1.05rem] leading-[1.7] mb-6">
        Most supplement companies send you back a PDF and wish you luck. We embed in your operation. We use your CRM. We email carriers from your domain. We show up as your team member. The carrier sees your company, not ours.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-400 text-[1.05rem] leading-[1.7] mb-6">
        That means faster approvals, smoother communication, and zero confusion about who's handling the claim.
      </p>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-8 list-none p-0 m-0">
        {features.map((f) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-100 text-[0.95rem]">
            <i class="ti ti-circle-check text-accent-teal text-[1.2rem] flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            <span>{f}</span>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Photo -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden" style="height: 600px;">
      <img
        src="/Firefly_CRM_flow.png"
        alt="How Precision Estimating works invisibly behind your brand"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center"
      />
    </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 items-center">

        <!-- Your Company -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-[320px] bg-[#1E3348] border border-accent/30 rounded-xl p-4 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 border border-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <i class="ti ti-building text-accent text-[1.2rem]" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mb-0.5">Carrier sees</div>
            <div class="text-white text-[0.95rem] font-semibold">Your Contractor Company</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-auto">
            <span class="text-[0.65rem] bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 text-accent px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">Visible</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow down -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
          <div class="w-px h-4 bg-accent/30"></div>
          <i class="ti ti-arrow-down text-accent/40 text-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>

        <!-- Precision (invisible layer) -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-[320px] relative">
          <div class="bg-accent-teal/[0.06] border border-accent-teal/25 border-dashed rounded-xl p-4 flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent-teal/10 border border-accent-teal/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <i class="ti ti-eye-off text-accent-teal text-[1.2rem]" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-[0.7rem] text-accent-teal/60 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mb-0.5">Working behind the scenes</div>
              <div class="text-accent-teal text-[0.95rem] font-semibold">Precision Estimating</div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-auto">
              <span class="text-[0.65rem] bg-accent-teal/10 border border-accent-teal/20 text-accent-teal px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">Invisible</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- What we do -->
          <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
            <div class="bg-[#1E3348] rounded-lg p-2 text-center">
              <i class="ti ti-file-text text-accent text-sm block mb-1" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span class="text-[0.65rem] text-slate-400">Estimates</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#1E3348] rounded-lg p-2 text-center">
              <i class="ti ti-search text-accent text-sm block mb-1" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span class="text-[0.65rem] text-slate-400">Supplements</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#1E3348] rounded-lg p-2 text-center">
              <i class="ti ti-messages text-accent text-sm block mb-1" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span class="text-[0.65rem] text-slate-400">Negotiations</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Arrow down -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-1">
          <div class="w-px h-4 bg-accent/30"></div>
          <i class="ti ti-arrow-down text-accent/40 text-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        </div>

        <!-- Insurance Carrier -->
        <div class="w-full max-w-[320px] bg-[#1E3348] border border-accent/30 rounded-xl p-4 flex items-center gap-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-accent/20 border border-accent/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
            <i class="ti ti-shield text-accent text-[1.2rem]" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-[0.7rem] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mb-0.5">Receives claim from</div>
            <div class="text-white text-[0.95rem] font-semibold">Insurance Carrier</div>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-auto">
            <span class="text-[0.65rem] bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 text-accent px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold">Visible</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-slate-400 text-[0.85rem] text-center">
        The carrier only sees your name. We're your back office.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
